# Stat Card SVG Template

## Overview

Template for single key metrics: hero numbers, KPI highlights, and social media stat cards. One number, one context line, maximum impact.

---

## Base Structure

```svg
<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 600 400" role="img">
  <title>[Metric Name]: [Value]</title>
  <desc>[Plain-text: The metric is X, which represents Y]</desc>

  <style>
    :root {
      --accent: #E94560;
      --secondary: #16213E;
      --bg: #FFFFFF;
      --text: #333333;
      --muted: #888888;
      --font: 'Inter', -apple-system, sans-serif;
    }

    text { font-family: var(--font); }
    .big-number { font-size: 96px; font-weight: 800; fill: var(--accent); }
    .metric-label { font-size: 22px; font-weight: 600; fill: var(--text); }
    .context { font-size: 15px; fill: var(--muted); }
    .trend-up { fill: #2ECC71; }
    .trend-down { fill: #E74C3C; }
    .source { font-size: 11px; fill: var(--muted); }
  </style>

  <rect width="600" height="400" fill="var(--bg)" rx="12" />

  <!-- Content goes here -->

  <!-- Brand Logo -->
  <g transform="translate(540, 360)" opacity="0.4">
    <!-- logo-mark -->
  </g>
</svg>
```

---

## Centered Stat Card

The simplest and most impactful layout:

```svg
<!-- Big number -->
<text x="300" y="180" class="big-number" text-anchor="middle">47%</text>

<!-- Label -->
<text x="300" y="225" class="metric-label" text-anchor="middle">Reduction in Deploy Time</text>

<!-- Context -->
<text x="300" y="260" class="context" text-anchor="middle">Down from 4.2 hours to 2.2 hours average</text>

<!-- Source -->
<text x="300" y="375" class="source" text-anchor="middle">Source: Internal metrics, Q3 2025</text>
```

---

## Stat Card with Trend Indicator

Add an up/down arrow to show direction:

```svg
<!-- Big number -->
<text x="300" y="170" class="big-number" text-anchor="middle">$2.4M</text>

<!-- Trend indicator (up arrow + percentage) -->
<g transform="translate(240, 195)">
  <polygon points="8,0 16,12 0,12" class="trend-up" />
  <text x="24" y="12" font-size="16" font-weight="600" class="trend-up">+18% MoM</text>
</g>

<!-- Label -->
<text x="300" y="240" class="metric-label" text-anchor="middle">Monthly Recurring Revenue</text>

<!-- Context -->
<text x="300" y="270" class="context" text-anchor="middle">Crossed $2M milestone in September</text>
```

For a downward trend:
```svg
<g transform="translate(240, 195)">
  <polygon points="0,0 16,0 8,12" class="trend-down" />
  <text x="24" y="12" font-size="16" font-weight="600" class="trend-down">-5% MoM</text>
</g>
```

