## Stat Card with Progress Ring

For metrics that represent progress toward a goal:

```svg
<!-- Background ring -->
<circle cx="300" cy="180" r="100" fill="none" stroke="var(--muted)" stroke-width="12"
        opacity="0.2" />

<!-- Progress ring (75% = 471 of 628 circumference) -->
<circle cx="300" cy="180" r="100" fill="none" stroke="var(--accent)" stroke-width="12"
        stroke-dasharray="471 628" stroke-dashoffset="0" stroke-linecap="round"
        transform="rotate(-90, 300, 180)" />

<!-- Number inside ring -->
<text x="300" y="175" font-size="48" font-weight="800" fill="var(--accent)"
      text-anchor="middle" font-family="var(--font)">75%</text>
<text x="300" y="205" class="context" text-anchor="middle">of goal</text>

<!-- Label below -->
<text x="300" y="320" class="metric-label" text-anchor="middle">Annual Revenue Target</text>
<text x="300" y="350" class="context" text-anchor="middle">$7.5M of $10M target reached</text>
```

**Calculating stroke-dasharray**: `circumference = 2 * pi * r = 2 * 3.14159 * 100 = 628`. For 75%: `628 * 0.75 = 471`.

