## Stat Card with Comparison

Show current value versus a benchmark:

```svg
<!-- Current value (large) -->
<text x="300" y="160" class="big-number" text-anchor="middle">4.8s</text>
<text x="300" y="195" class="metric-label" text-anchor="middle">Average Page Load</text>

<!-- Comparison line -->
<line x1="150" y1="230" x2="450" y2="230" stroke="var(--muted)" stroke-width="1" />

<!-- Benchmark (smaller, muted) -->
<text x="300" y="270" font-size="14" fill="var(--muted)" text-anchor="middle"
      font-family="var(--font)">Industry average: 8.2s</text>
<text x="300" y="295" font-size="14" fill="var(--accent)" text-anchor="middle"
      font-family="var(--font)" font-weight="600">41% faster than industry</text>
```

